ygData.subject: Re: Lvl 8 pet spell
ygData.msgSnippet: Important note about the trip to High Hold Pass. DO NOT PASS THE BANK. You think you are safe inside and exploring is fun..... But I made the trip at 5th level
ygData.messageBody:
Important note about the trip to High Hold Pass.
DO NOT PASS THE BANK.
You think you are safe inside and exploring is fun.....
But I made the trip at 5th level and the prisoners ate my lunch.
They are just past the bank so be careful.
Apparently the prisoner's are under house arrest and the cells arent
relaly locked )


Scott ( aka Fystro of Solusek Ro)




"Daniel Stock" <argovian@...> on 04/21/99 04:59:00 PM

Please respond to eqenchanters@onelist.com

To: eqenchanters@onelist.com
cc: (bcc: Scott McGougan/OpenSys/Star)
Subject: [eqenchanters] Re: Lvl 8 pet spell




From: "Daniel Stock" <argovian@...>

Its called Miyrl's ... <SP?> And near freeport goto High Pass.

1st bit of advice.. GET A GUIDE. If you cannot, I warn you, DO NOT
let Invisibilty wear off.. I tried to do this myself the other night.

It took me 3 hours and dying 5 times to FINALLY get there..

2ndly, When your in High Pass.. Keep INIVIS ON. THere are guards and
yes it looks safe, Do not be decived. Gnoll Bashers/Shamans Orc
Scouts Etc Spawn here.. MANY at a time, lots of trains.. Watch your 6.

I got a lvl 20 Enchanter to help me get there.. he took me to the
vendor who sells it.. (Once your in High Pass you gotta go into
another zone with the NPC's No spawn there.. safe for med or whatever)
